message.body: Would the boys be able to do some yard work this afternoon?
I just got up !!!! The meds make me feel very Yucky in the mornings... I will talk to them in a few minutes and get back to you ASAP. As far as I know at least one of them is available.
Ok let me know. Thanks! How are you?
What time? I am up and down.
Shenandoah is ready to come soon.
I am not at home. I can go home but have to go to pt at noon. Call me, ok?
Did shenandoa get home ok? I just got home.
